main event: A circular flying object was sighted at a high altitude in Bohemia, Maryland on July 26, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for 15 minutes but did not return.
The object was described as a 'high flying, reddish, glowing object'.
The report concluded that the data was insufficient for evaluation.
The document appears to be related to Project Blue Book, the Air Force's investigation of unidentified flying objects.
The observer wanted to inform the authorities about the sighting and requested instructions.
